      <h1 class="title">
      “A internet veio para bagunçar o coreto do intermediário” – Entrevista JornalismoB
  </h1>
  <span class="publishing-info">
  <span class="date">
    decembro 9, 2014 11:28
  </span>
  <span class="author">
    , by <a href="http://softwarelivre.org/branco">Marcelo D&#39;Elia Branco</a>
  </span>
  <span class="comments">
     - <a href="/branco/blog/“a-internet-veio-para-baguncar-o-coreto-do-intermediario”-–-entrevista-jornalismob#comments_list"><span class='comment-count hide'>0</span><span class='comment-count-write-out'>no comments yet</span></a>
